      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "&quot;gradle idea&quot; is needed only to generate the required files. Though the recent versions of Idea use &quot;directory-based&quot; project structure, so the file generation is no longer necessary. With or without file generation, from inside the Idea the project is run the same way. It is a pity that we don&#39;t have enough flexibility here."
