    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>IntelliJ interacts with Gradle via the Gradle tooling API, which always uses the daemon. \n<strong>i.e. There is no way to turn it off.</strong></p>\n\n<p>What you could do (after filing a bug report) is not to use the IntelliJ Gradle integration but instead generate IntelliJ project files with </p>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p><code>gradle idea</code></p>\n</blockquote>\n"
